---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about CapCity Presents, the independent Olympia music presenter booking local and touring artists across the South Sound.">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container split">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
        <h1>About CapCity Presents</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="panel prose">
        <p>CapCity Presents grew out of Olympia's DIY and independent music world and keeps working to connect artists, venues, and audiences.</p>
        <p>Founded in Olympia in 2015, CapCity was built to give touring musicians a clearer local stop and to make local promotion feel more connected.</p>
        <p>CapCity works across venues and lineups rather than from a single room, with a focus on matching the right artists to the right space and crowd.</p>
        <p>The goal is simple: better shows, stronger turnout, and a stronger case that Olympia matters as a live-music stop in its own right.</p>
        <div class="actions"><a class="button primary" href="/events/">See upcoming shows</a><a class="button" href="/contact/">Contact CapCity</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
